ition offers corrections of mistakes and didactical improvements.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 4aAussagenlogik. 4aLogik. 4aMetalogik. 4aPrädikatenlogik. 4aSemantik.  aSemantics.  alogic.  ametalogic.  apredicate logic.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2020z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2020z9783110704648oZDB-23-DPH0 cEPUBz97831106974760 cprintz978311069714840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311069739140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110697391423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110697391.jpg  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Ebook Package 2020b2020  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-DPHb2020